1. *Šest* puta sam rekao da neću da idem tamo. (I said six times that I won't go there.)
2. Treba da odem *šest* puta do kraja meseca. (I need to go six times until the end of the month.)
3. Brat i ja smo *šest* godina stariji. (My brother and I are six years older.)
4. *Šest* meseci sam proveo u inostranstvu. (I spent six months abroad.)
5. *Šest* osoba je bilo na večeri. (There were six people at the dinner.)
6. *Šest* je moj omiljeni broj. (Six is my favorite number.)